Value of denoise
1.00 = completely ignore the masked area
0.70-0.85 = good for body posture reference in the masked area

nodes.title: Load destination (right-click to mask the area)
Load face if it's a person
Tips
widgets_values:
Disable Face Swap Unit if you don't want to swap face, e.g., transfering non-human or encountering errors about ReActor nodes.

Disable Post-Processing Unit if the result image is too sharp.

If it swaps face to the wrong person, you can manually set in the Face Swap Unit. (see input_face_order)
